data.description:
Escape to your very own sanctuary nestled in the heart of vibrant Thornton, Colorado! Boasting a resplendent blend of modern convenience and timeless charm, this stunning two-story home unfolds over an oversized lot, creating an enchanting retreat.
Step into a warm, inviting living room adorned with a soaring vaulted ceiling. Its seamlessly adjacent dining room promises memorable family dinners and heartwarming holidays. The nearby kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's delight with its stainless-steel refrigerator, dishwasher, and the rare luxury of a double oven. A spacious pantry and a cozy breakfast nook complete the heart of the home. Next, you'll find the snug family room, where the crackle of a gas fireplace creates an irresistible ambiance. Step through the adjacent door to be greeted by a serene back patio, perfect for those morning coffees or evening drinks.
Upstairs, retreat to your tranquil master suite - a dreamy haven featuring a lofty 12-foot vaulted ceiling, a luxurious 5-piece en-suite bath, and a spacious walk-in closet. Two more beautifully designed bedrooms and another full bath round off this private space. Downstairs, the partially finished basement invites you to transform it to your liking, with a flexible space ideal for a media room or home office, an extra bedroom, and ample storage. The true gem of this residence lies in its backyard oasis. Indulge in the serenity of your own private park, with a picturesque gazebo overlooking a captivating water feature. Savor the sweetness of summer with pear and peach trees! HOA fees include clubhouse, pool and tennis court use. Situated with easy access to groceries, retail, restaurants, and the I-25 for your commuting needs, this home strikes the perfect balance between tranquil retreat and city convenience. Don't let this unique opportunity pass you by. Come see it today! You won't just be buying a home; you'll be investing in a lifestyle.
